## Usage Patterns

### Basic Usage

```tsx
() => (
  <div>
    <InfoLink
      message="Goodbye, world!"
      automationId="basic"
      onClick={action('Click from InfoLink')}
      onKeyDown={action('Keypress from InfoLink')}
      onTooltipClose={action('Tooltip closed')}
    >
      Hello, world!
    </InfoLink>
  </div>
)
```

### Rich Content Child

```tsx
() => (
  <div>
    <InfoLink automationId="richChild" message="Goodbye, world!">
      Hello,
      <strong style={{ fontWeight: 'bolder' }}>world!</strong>
    </InfoLink>
  </div>
)
```

### Rich Content Child Message

```tsx
() => (
  <div>
    <InfoLink
      automationId="richAll"
      message={
        <div>
          Goodbye,
          <strong style={{ fontWeight: 'bolder' }}>world!</strong>
        </div>
      }
    >
      Hello,
      <strong style={{ fontWeight: 'bolder' }}>world!</strong>
    </InfoLink>
  </div>
)
```

### Rich Content Message With Title

```tsx
() => (
  <div>
    <InfoLink
      automationId="richMessage"
      title="Hello"
      size="medium"
      message={
        <div>
          Goodbye,
          <strong style={{ fontWeight: 'bolder' }}>world!</strong>
        </div>
      }
    >
      Hello, world!
    </InfoLink>
  </div>
)
```

### Customize Tooltip Offset

```tsx
() => (
  <div>
    <InfoLink
      automationId="tooltipOffset"
      message="Account can't earn interest if there's no money in it."
      tooltipOffsetSkidding={-18}
      tooltipOffsetDistance={5}
    >
      $0
    </InfoLink>
  </div>
)
```

### Enable Click Away

```tsx
() => (
  <div
    style={{
      display: 'flex',
      justifyContent: 'center',
      alignItems: 'center',
      width: '100%',
      height: '100vh'
    }}
  >
    <div>
      <InfoLink
        enableClickAway={false}
        title="Some sort of title"
        message={
          <span>
            <b>enableClickAway</b> prop is false. So I would not close when you
            click away.
          </span>
        }
      >
        EnableClickAway false
      </InfoLink>

      <br aria-hidden />
      <br aria-hidden />
      <br aria-hidden />
      <br aria-hidden />

      <InfoLink
        enableClickAway
        title="Some sort of title"
        message={
          <span>
            <b>enableClickAway</b> prop is true. So I would close when you click
            away.
          </span>
        }
      >
        EnableClickAway true
      </InfoLink>
    </div>
  </div>
)
```

